::Prowl/Annihilator/Killer::

Killer yells as trees start falling all around him. Maybe it hadn't been such 
a good idea to attack these two maximals. He turns to run, but a tree branch 
hits him over the head, knocking him out.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Annihilator thrown into Iron Raptor's head by Tritan's shot and knocked 
backwards by the impact. He flies up, his jetpack barely pulling off the 
power strain.

Once sufficiantly high, he opens fire on the three bots on the ground.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Prowl rubs his head as Iron Raptor's claws blot out his view of Annihilator. 
He stands up, rubbing his head.

"Warning. Damage level reaching critical. Mech fluid lever low." Prowl's 
internal computer reports in an annoying tone.

Prowl swears silently, rolling out from under Iron Raptor's hand and firing 
up at Annihilator.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Annihilator groans as Prowl's shot hits him, going up through his stomach. 
The predacon slowly attemps to land when Tritan's shots hit him, sending him 
flying off into the distance.
